課程教材 Course Material
	     1. Chapters 2, 3, 5, 7, 8, 10, 13, 14, 15, 16 of Caculus: One and Several Variables 10th edition by Salas, Etgen and Hille.
 2. Chapters 3, 4, 5 of Linear Algebra and its applications 4th edition by David C. Lay
 3. Linear Algebra Lecture Notes by S. Paul Smith 
        

參考書目 References
