備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
        無    

核心能力 Competence
□ 掌握連續與逼進的能力
 Ability to handle continuity phenomena and approximations.
■ 處理數字及符號運算的能力
 Ability to operate with symbols and digits.
■ 透視形像與空間的能力
 Ability to visualize space, shape, and images.
□ 利用計算機處理數學的能力
 Ability of using computer to do mathematics.
□ 應用隨機理論的能力
 Ability to apply stochastic mathematics.
□ 處理大量數據的能力
 Ability to handle large amount of data.
□ 處理離散型數學的能力
 Ability to do mathematics relating to discrete models.
□ 獨立研究的能力
 Ability to do independent studies of mathematics.
□ 使用計算機的能力
 Abilities to use computer as a tool.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       坐標系, 直線, 曲線, 基本矩陣運算.Coordinate systems, lines and curves and elementary matrix algebra.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Differentiation and integration formulas. Conic sections; Polar, cylindrical, and spherical coordinates. Basis, subspaces, and dimensions. Matrices and relations to linear transformations. Singularities and invertibilities of matrices; Determinants. Eigenspaces and diagonalizabilites. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Review of Elementary Mathematics, Inequalities, Analytics Geometry, Functions2Limits and Continuity3Limits and Continuity, The Pinching Theorem,Trigonometric Limits 4The Derivative, Differentiation Formulas, The Chain Rule, Differentiating the Trigonometric Functions, Implicit Differentiation, Rational Powers5The Derivative, Differentiation Formulas, The Chain Rule, Differentiating the Trigonometric Functions, Implicit Differentiation, Rational Powers6Integration, The Definite Integral of a Continuous Function, THe Fundamental Theorem of Integral Calculus, Indefinite Integrals7The Transcendental Functions, The Logarithm Function, Arbitrary Powers, Inverse Trigonometric Functions8Integration by Parts, Powers and Products of Trigonometric Functions, Trigonometric Substitutions, Rational Functions, Partial Fractions9Conic Sections, Polar Coordinates, Parametric Equations, Vector Calculus10Vector Calculus, Midterm Exam 111Vectors in Three-Dimensional Space, The Dot Product, The Cross Product, Determinants12Determinants, Vector Calculus, Functions of Several Variables, Partial Derivatives13Functions of Several Variables, Partial Derivatives, Gradients, Level Sets, Tangent Planes, Hessian Matrix, Local Extreme Values14Determinants, Inverstible Matrices and Inverses15Cramer's Rule, Eigenvectors and Eigenvalues, The Charateristic equation, Diagonalization16The Vector Spaces, Subspaces17Linear Dependence and Independence18Linear Dependence and Independence; Final Exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


